OL,3,CGuernsey gas prices to rise by 10% in
OL,4,C2025
OL,6,FGuernsey households will see their gas
OL,7,Fbills rise by 10% from the start of
OL,8,Fnext year.
OL,10,FIslands Energy Group, the parent
OL,11,Fcompany of Guernsey Energy, announced
OL,12,Fthe price hike that will come into
OL,13,Feffect from 1 January 2025.
OL,15,FThe gas company says that this will
OL,16,Fmean the average household will pay an
OL,17,Fadditional #9.37 a month.
OL,19,FThe rise has been attributed to
OL,20,Fincreasing global gas prices.
