OL,3,CGuernsey gas prices to rise by 10% in
OL,4,C2025
OL,6,FIt follows Guernsey Water also
OL,7,Fannouncing water bill increases
OL,8,Fbetween #5 and #8 for their customers.
OL,10,FDarryl Goddard, Managing Director of
OL,11,FGuernsey Energy explains:
OL,12,F"Geopolitical events across Europe
OL,13,Fhave continued to impact the price of
OL,14,Fwholesale gas over the last 12 months.
OL,16,F"Energy markets are subject to a
OL,17,Fvariety of complex influences which
OL,18,Fimpact our supply chain and keep the
OL,19,Fcost of services that are crucial to
OL,20,Fthe supply of gas high.
