OL,6,F"We understand that tariff increases
OL,7,Fcan be difficult for our customers to
OL,8,Fmanage, but given these circumstances,
OL,9,Fthey unfortunately cannot be avoided.
OL,11,F"We're continuing to invest heavily
OL,12,Facross our network and drive forward a
OL,13,Fcomprehensive maintenance programme."
OL,15,FMr Goddard says that vulnerable
OL,16,Fcustomers can find additional support
OL,17,Fand alternate payment plans through
OL,18,Ftheir Priority Care scheme.
